int16_t FaultBlock

Fault block identifier.

  • Set to fault block for location in Earth Vision model
  • Set to 0 for locations outside the domain.
  • Set to INTERIORBLOCK for interior octants that contain values that are the average of its children.

  • Set to INTERIORZONE for interior octants that contain values that are the averages of its children.
